reviewText: If you like Townshend you will like this.  I have video edition. 45 minutes in length, the work is a short film with excellent actors, includind Townshend as himself. It chronicles the further adventures of Jimmy from Quad. ('According to Townshend.). Jimmy is now in his 30s and coming to terms with a life of limited opportunity, or so he seems to think.  It's relationship to album is similar to Quad's album to Quads film.  I obtained by copy from a close out sell of a video store. Additional song also on video written to encourage attending adult night school.
